Franklin Mutual agrees to buy Cityscape options . Cityscape Financial Corp said Monday that Franklin Mutual Advisers Inc bought the options held by three of Cityscape ' s principal shareholders . The options represent the right to buy 4 . 14 million outstanding shares of Cityscape ' s common stock . Cityscape Financial granted certain registration rights to Franklin Mutual Advisers , upon completion of the deal , scheduled to close on January 7 , 1997 . No further terms were disclosed . Cityscape Financial , based Elmsford , N . Y . , is a consumer finance company . - - New York Newsdesk 212 - 859 - 1610 . 
